{"id": "562595", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=562595", "title": "Claw (gnoll)", "text": "Claw was the &lt;a href=\"Woodpaw%20clan\"&gt;Woodpaw&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"gnoll\"&gt;gnoll&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"gnoll%20brute\"&gt;brute&lt;/a&gt;. He was a close friend to &lt;a href=\"Gnaw%20%28gnoll%29\"&gt;Gnaw&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen the hyena suddenly left the Woodpaw lands, he didn't care and agreed with Matriarch &lt;a href=\"Greasefang\"&gt;Greasefang&lt;/a&gt; to be a good thing. He also agreed with her when she said that the cut trees were a result of the &lt;a href=\"Feral%20Scar\"&gt;Feral Scar&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"yeti\"&gt;yeti&lt;/a&gt;s. In order to convince the gnolls that the trees were cut instead of being pushed, Gnaw showed Claw trees. Gnaw told him that &lt;a href=\"Hackle\"&gt;Hackle&lt;/a&gt; is right about Greasefang being wrong, but Claw initially cuffed Gnaw, and believed Greasefang right. Despite this, Claw did take Greasefang to show her the cut trees, but the two never returned to their clan as they were killed. &lt;a href=\"Jaggal\"&gt;Jaggal&lt;/a&gt; blamed the yetis for their deaths. They were succeeded by Gnaw and &lt;a href=\"Jawstretcher\"&gt;Jawstretcher&lt;/a&gt;.\nSpeculation.\nAlthough not stated, he was very likely the father of Jaggal, as he was the clan's brute when Greasefang was their matriarch."}
