ising &lt;a href=\"Frostbrood%20Destroyer\"&gt;Frostbrood Destroyer&lt;/a&gt;s to send to the &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Vanguard\"&gt;Argent Vanguard&lt;/a&gt;.\nDuring &lt;a href=\"Death%20Rising\"&gt;Death Rising&lt;/a&gt;, the area was infected with &lt;a href=\"Gloomshroom\"&gt;Gloomshroom&lt;/a&gt; which grew bigger among cadavers.\nScourgeholme digsite.\nScourgeholme is a nerubian &lt;a href=\"archaeology\"&gt;archaeology&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"dig%20site\"&gt;dig site&lt;/a&gt;."}
