{"id": "36429", "revid": "46586549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=36429", "title": "Reyna Stonebranch", "text": "Reyna Stonebranch is a &lt;a href=\"dwarf\"&gt;dwarf&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"herbalism%20trainer\"&gt;herbalism trainer&lt;/a&gt; located in the shop &lt;a href=\"Ironforge%20Physician\"&gt;Ironforge Physician&lt;/a&gt;, in the southern section of the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Forge\"&gt;Great Forge&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ironforge\"&gt;Ironforge&lt;/a&gt;. \nFollowing the instructions from the &lt;a href=\"Tablets%20of%20the%20Earth\"&gt;tablet&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Ulduar\"&gt;Ulduar&lt;/a&gt;, Reyna created the liquid that was intended for &lt;a href=\"Magni\"&gt;Magni&lt;/a&gt; to communicate with &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;, but instead he was turned into diamond.\nQuotes.\nI can instruct you in herbalism. Interested?"}
{"id": "269555", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=269555", "title": "Reynah Firecaster", "text": "Reynah Firecaster was a &lt;a href=\"blood%20elf\"&gt;blood elf&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"mage\"&gt;mage&lt;/a&gt; who, with &lt;a href=\"Barnabas%20Grell\"&gt;Barnabas Grell&lt;/a&gt; attempted to avenge their loved ones who were killed by the &lt;a href=\"Scarlet%20Crusade\"&gt;Scarlet Crusade&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nWhile hunting in &lt;a href=\"Winterspring\"&gt;Winterspring&lt;/a&gt;, Reynah received word from &lt;a href=\"Sovok\"&gt;an ally&lt;/a&gt; from the &lt;a href=\"Alterac%20Valley\"&gt;Alterac Valley&lt;/a&gt; that her brother, &lt;a href=\"Rinn%20Firecaster\"&gt;Rinn Firecaster&lt;/a&gt; was killed by the Scarlet Crusade. When she arrived to &lt;a href=\"Undercity\"&gt;Undercity&lt;/a&gt; she begged &lt;a href=\"Varimathras\"&gt;Varimathras&lt;/a&gt; for an audience with &lt;a href=\"Sylvanas%20Windrunner\"&gt;Sylvanas Windrunner&lt;/a&gt; demanding justice for her brother who was killed in their lands. Varimathras however brushed her off, telling her that Sylvanas has more to worry about than one death and if she wants justice done do it herself. On her way out, she accidentally bumped into Barnabas Grell and the two had an argument, threatening to kill one and other if they saw each other again. After leaving Undercity, Reynah hunted down Scarlets until she ran into Barnabas. Before the two killed each other, they came to an understanding that they both were hunting the same targets and decided that, until they killed the Scarlet leader &lt;a href=\"Renee%20Lauer\"&gt;Renee Lauer&lt;/a&gt;, they would work together.\nThe two attacked the Scarlet camp and managed to capture Renee. However, the two began arguing over who would deal the killing blow, allowing Renee's allies to arrive and incapacitate both of them. Before their execution Barnabas and Reynah told the Scarlets they vowed vengeance over the deaths of their loved ones and asked Renee why would she kill innocents. When Renee responded that the &lt;a href=\"Forsaken\"&gt;Forsaken&lt;/a&gt; and the blood elves were a disease infesting &lt;a href=\"Lordaeron\"&gt;human lands&lt;/a&gt; Reynah attacked the surrounding Scarlets with her fire magic, until they were cornered and injured explosives. Reynah was killed when a Scarlet broke her neck, while Barnabas was killed by decapitation. Moments later, Forsaken led by Sylvanas Windrunner and Varimathras killed the entire camp and raised Renee Lauer as one of the undead."}
