{"id": "247518", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=247518", "title": "Inside the Frozen Citadel (Alliance)", "text": "Objectives.\nEnter &lt;a href=\"Forge%20of%20Souls\"&gt;The Forge of Souls&lt;/a&gt; from the side of &lt;a href=\"Icecrown%20Citadel\"&gt;Icecrown Citadel&lt;/a&gt; and find Lady &lt;a href=\"Jaina%20Proudmoore\"&gt;Jaina Proudmoore&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\n&lt;Class&gt;! Come close quickly, I must have a word!\nMy patron, the Lady Jaina Proudmoore, has uncovered a hole in the defenses of Icecrown Citadel into a place she referred to as \"The Forge of Souls.\" She sent word before she left for me to find any help that I could... and, well, I was hoping that might be you.\nPlease, find her there as soon as she can.\nCompletion.\n&lt;Name&gt;! I'm so glad you've come.\nWe've been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we're to avoid &lt;a href=\"Arthas\"&gt;Arthas&lt;/a&gt;' notice.\nRewards.\nYou will receive: (+ at max level)\nNotes.\nApprentice Nelphi patrols around &lt;a href=\"Dalaran\"&gt;Dalaran&lt;/a&gt;, stopping in the &lt;a href=\"Silver%20Enclave\"&gt;Silver Enclave&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Legerdemain%20Lounge\"&gt;Legerdemain Lounge&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Dalaran%20Merchant%27s%20Bank\"&gt;Dalaran Merchant's Bank&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Krasus%27%20Landing\"&gt;Krasus' Landing&lt;/a&gt;.\nTo get to the &lt;a href=\"Forge%20of%20Souls\"&gt;Forge of Souls&lt;/a&gt; (52.5, 89.4), fly west out of Dalaran towards &lt;a href=\"Icecrown%20Citadel\"&gt;Icecrown Citadel&lt;/a&gt;. On the high parapet just to the southwest of the citadel's main entrance (look for the first 'c' of 'Icecrown' on the in-game zone map) is a small entrance marked by &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Commander\"&gt;Argent Commander&lt;/a&gt;s astride &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Hippogryph\"&gt;Argent Hippogryph&lt;/a&gt;s. Inside is the &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20Halls\"&gt;Frozen Halls&lt;/a&gt;, a small sanctuary inside the citadel guarded by commanders of the &lt;a href=\"Ebon%20Blade%20Commander\"&gt;Ebon Blade&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Argent%20Commander\"&gt;Argent Crusade&lt;/a&gt;. There are three wings of the halls: the &lt;a href=\"Forge%20of%20Souls\"&gt;Forge of Souls&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Halls%20of%20Reflection\"&gt;Halls of Reflection&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=\"Pit%20of%20Saron\"&gt;Pit of Saron&lt;/a&gt;, clockwise from the north."}
