{"id": "192499", "revid": "40385772", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=192499", "title": "Insignia of the Alliance (Druid)", "text": "Insignia of the Alliance is a &lt;a href=\"quality\"&gt;quality&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"PvP\"&gt;PvP&lt;/a&gt; reward that removes all movement impairing effects but does not prevent them from being reapplied. Usable even if the effect would normally prevent trinket use. This item is popular for level 19 &lt;a href=\"twink\"&gt;twink&lt;/a&gt;s for use in &lt;a href=\"Warsong%20Gulch\"&gt;Warsong Gulch&lt;/a&gt;, where being able to break &lt;a href=\"root\"&gt;root&lt;/a&gt;ing can bring a victory.\nSource.\nThis &lt;a href=\"PvP%20rewards\"&gt;PvP reward&lt;/a&gt; item can be purchased from in &lt;a href=\"Champions%27%20Hall\"&gt;Champions' Hall&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Stormwind\"&gt;Stormwind&lt;/a&gt; for .\nNotes.\nThe old druid insignia only removed charm, fear, and stun. "}
