{"id": "132106", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=132106", "title": "Inspecting the Ruins (Alliance)", "text": "Objectives.\nSpeak to &lt;a href=\"Inspector%20Tarem\"&gt;Inspector Tarem&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Shady%20Rest%20Inn\"&gt;Shady Rest Inn&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nPoor &lt;a href=\"James%20Hyal\"&gt;James&lt;/a&gt; never recovered from the destruction of the Shady Rest and the murder of his family. The boys and I are doing what we can to find the monsters who did this.\nI've sent our best investigator, Inspector Tarem, out to the ruins, but this is too big a job for any one man. If you'd lend Tarem a hand, we'd appreciate it. Light knows, we'd all like to be out there helping.\nThe main road will lead you to the inn, but take care. Your journey will take you beyond the protection of my soldiers.\nCompletion.\nIt's good to see that &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Garran%20Vimes\"&gt;Captain Vimes&lt;/a&gt; is finally assigning others to this investigation.\nI've used a reflective powder to dust the area. It will reveal suspicious objects and markings, helping you to focus your efforts. Look over anything the dust illuminates.\nGains.\nYou will receive: 330 XP (or at 70)\nNotes.\nThis quest was added in &lt;a href=\"Patch%202.3.0\"&gt;Patch 2.3.0&lt;/a&gt; as a more obvious means of getting people to the &lt;a href=\"Shady%20Rest%20Inn\"&gt;Shady Rest Inn&lt;/a&gt; to pick up the three quests out there.\nWhen completing this quest, Tarem gives you the buff \"Spread Reflective Dust\", which lasts for 2 minutes. While buffed, 3 arrows appear in the general area. Hoofprints are next to Tarem, a Theramore Guard Badge is on the floor of the Inn, and a Black Shield is over the fireplace. Inspect each of the items to pick up a new quest. Players can ask Tarem to reapply the buff if necessary.\nProgression.\nThis is part of &lt;a href=\"The%20Shady%20Rest%20Inn%20quest%20chain\"&gt;The Shady Rest Inn quest chain&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "146572", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=146572", "title": "Inspecting the Ruins (Horde)", "text": "Objectives.\nInvestigate the &lt;a href=\"Shady%20Rest%20Inn\"&gt;Shady Rest Inn&lt;/a&gt; in at the border of the &lt;a href=\"Barrens\"&gt;Barrens&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Dustwallow%20Marsh\"&gt;Dustwallow Marsh&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nIf you follow the road south from the village, and then west toward the Barrens, you'll come across the ruins of the Shady Rest Inn.\n&lt;a href=\"Theramore\"&gt;Theramore&lt;/a&gt; has sent an investigator to discover how the inn met its fate. I had a man placed in that inn as a &lt;a href=\"spy\"&gt;spy&lt;/a&gt; and I don't trust in the competence of these &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt;s to uncover what happened.\nWhatever you find, don't give a scrap of it to that investigator. We'll handle this ourselves.\nCompletion.\n&lt;The inspector regards you with what can only be disdain and distrust.&gt;\nLeave this place be, errand boy, or I'll be sure to bring a contingent of guard with me next time to sink the lesson home.\nNotes.\nWhen completing this quest, Tarem gives you the buff \"Spread Reflective Dust\", which lasts for 2 minutes. While buffed, 3 arrows appear in the general area. Hoofprints are next to Tarem, a Theramore Guard Badge is on the floor of the Inn, and a Black Shield is over the fireplace. Inspect each of the items to pick up a new quest. Players can ask Tarem to reapply the buff if necessary.\nOriginal version.\nSpeak to Inspector Tarem at the Shady Rest Inn.\nIf you follow the road south from the village, and then west toward the Barrens, you'll come across the ruins of the Shady Rest Inn.\nTheramore has sent an investigator to discover how the inn met its fate. Normally, I'd advise you to steer clear, but we have orders from Orgrimmar to 'assist' in the investigation.\nAccept any help the Theramore investigator offers, even feed him a tidbit or two of information if you'd like, but save your real findings for me.\n&lt;The inspector regards you with what can only be distrust.&gt;\nI've been told that you're to... aid in this investigation. Very well, then.\nI've been using this powder to search the ruins for clues that might help identify the attackers. It will illuminate anything that might have been involved in the attack. Don't hesitate to examine anything that looks suspicious.\nProgression.\nThis is part of &lt;a href=\"The%20Shady%20Rest%20Inn%20quest%20chain\"&gt;The Shady Rest Inn quest chain&lt;/a&gt;."}
